name: STASE(III)
description: They buried me the day before my wedding. Me, I wanted to have my head in the stars, and my feet treading the ground of another planet. I wanted to learn another language. I wanted to paint with my eyes, make music with my hair, write with my mouth, sculpt the wind with my hands. I wanted to be loved like a beating heart in another chest and live my fairy tale without thinking about the end.
